Name: Average time from 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by ADMINISTRATION' to 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by ADMINISTRATION'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Total time for 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by ADMINISTRATION' to reach 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Minimum time from 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by ADMINISTRATION' to 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER'

Name: Average waiting time to 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by ADMINISTRATION' after 'Declaration SAVED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SAVED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Total resolution time of 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by ADMINISTRATION'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by ADMINISTRATION and the end of the case

Name: Minimum time for 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by ADMINISTRATION' to transition to 'Request Payment'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Total time it takes 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by ADMINISTRATION' after 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Average time for 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by ADMINISTRATION' in cases leading to 'Payment Handled'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Total time from 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by ADMINISTRATION' to 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER'

Name: Minimum resolution time of 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by ADMINISTRATION' in successful claims
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time to 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by ADMINISTRATION' from 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' in re-submission cases
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by ADMINISTRATION' to 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' in cases that are eventually approved
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER'
